                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.6363/721: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Robert Murray</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-09-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 7, 1920</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Chief of the Division of Mexican Affairs of Department of State will be
                    pleased to discuss with Mr. Pesqueira, matters mentioned in your telegram of
                    September 5th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bainbridge Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
